586
00:38:26,480 --> 00:38:27,920
-Halo. -(Tuan Luo.)

587
00:38:28,760 --> 00:38:29,760
(Ini Ren Xin Zheng.)

588
00:38:30,280 --> 00:38:31,080
Ren,

589
00:38:31,960 --> 00:38:33,200
