590
00:38:33,560 --> 00:38:34,400
Aku tahu.

591
00:38:34,720 --> 00:38:35,520
Tuan Luo,

592
00:38:36,160 --> 00:38:38,040
Saya sedang dalam perjalanan ke Wuhan.

593
00:38:38,480 --> 00:38:39,840
Bagaimana situasi di sana?

594
00:38:40,400 --> 00:38:41,557
(Tidak bagus. Jangan kemari.)

595
00:38:41,640 --> 00:38:43,077
Dengar, banyak rekan kita

596
00:38:43,160 --> 00:38:45,280
di bagian bedah telah terinfeksi.

597
00:38:46,680 --> 00:38:47,880
Departemen penyakit dalam?

598
00:38:48,360 --> 00:38:49,560
Itu sama saja.

599
00:38:49,880 --> 00:38:51,277
(Persediaan medis langka.)

600
00:38:51,360 --> 00:38:53,720
(Para petinggi sudah mengoordinasikan dukungan.)

